Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.24,0:00:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.08,0:00:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.55,0:00:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.66,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.80,0:00:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.12,0:01:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.39,0:01:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.41,0:01:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.25,0:01:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個都很忙,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,不用勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年我本來就打算\N只跟音無家的人去掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.36,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的這是什麼話啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們畢竟也是親人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.93,0:01:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過年也只是寄個賀年卡\N都沒有去登門拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.21,0:02:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁這種時候\N當要去露個臉打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說,明明知道卻沒去的話\N反而更失禮,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼明天一點鐘\N在音無家集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要從音無家直接過去掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是惣一郎的忌日嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是妳娘家的老媽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.16,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她想假裝去掃墓\N然後藉機跟我談再婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,對了,跟妳借點醬油好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家的醬油剛好用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請拿,就放在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.01,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我借一下囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳真的不打算再婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.02,0:02:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,況且在墳前談這種事\N未免太失禮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.15,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是那麼說沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是夠了,我才不想再婚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.40,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#52 惣一郎請原諒我!\N響子含淚的再婚宣言!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員她怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真悠哉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.54,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們去年好像是利用孫子的話題\N跟我提再婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.78,0:04:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年呢?不過沒用的\N不管說什麼我都不會認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從響子開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經四年了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,時間過得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年也是個大晴天,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都是託您的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,所以我嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.10,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?\N怎麼都沒提到再婚的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人要補票啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳今年蠻沈穩的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這有什麼辦法,那孩子太固執了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說太多的話,她反而會更賭氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛,實在跟某人好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天真是好睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是問我爸媽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天什麼都沒提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我去澡堂洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.33,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代因為擔心我\N而特地等我回來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎麼說,這樣實在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,託妳的福\N沒有繼續牽扯下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說了些什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟妳說了\N他們都沒提到再婚的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.38,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是問這個啦\N妳向妳老公說了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是掃墓掃呆了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是不是因為\N今年妳爸媽沒有囉嗦唸妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.73,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以回想起了\N很多美好的回憶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不知道這是算長還是算短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我真的無法忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.22,0:08:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出門了,男子的髪髻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近總覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打完球後去喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.88,0:08:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比較少想起惣一郎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打了四谷名片上寫的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果是一個叫莉加的女孩接的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的打過去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,還跟對方說了話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房客們每天都很開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員\N管理員,妳來看一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了,這個水龍頭很討厭耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且工作讓我忙到\N根本沒時間難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得我一定很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.78,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一副無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣漸漸把惣一郎給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.39,0:11:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕女孩的皮膚果然不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.56,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳要出門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個不能給你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找惣一郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.86,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忌日那天才去祭拜過而已\N怎麼又去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真的說要去找惣一郎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,一臉想不開的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還拿著一個這麼大的細長包裹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細長包裹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該不太可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你急急忙忙要去哪裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟妳說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也認為不可能\N不過,還是小心一點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.43,0:13:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來\N管理員最近都沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.53,0:13:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也察覺到啦\N從掃墓回來就變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事就跟我們說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她實在太見外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.31,0:13:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,光男嗎?\N是我,茶茶丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.19,0:13:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得應該是這一帶吧\N畢竟已經很久沒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要這個,還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.36,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這裡沒錯啊\N會不會被四谷耍了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要躲起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細長包裹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,這是干瓢壽司捲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡沒有切整條咬著吃,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,這是茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.03,0:15:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是把你忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.27,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天來是想整理一下心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?不會吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之快去醫院,就這樣直接去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,郁子也快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.19,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前想起這件事\N總會難過得無法抬起頭來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,現在比起想起悲傷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我想到開心的事時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會開始哭了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你要死掉呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.62,0:17:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你還活著\N我就不用受這種折磨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來她還是無法忘記啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.42,0:17:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很希望能永遠懷念著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.26,0:17:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然我現在還是想著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.26,0:18:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是身旁活著的人們\N漸漸進入我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.14,0:18:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天\N我會把你沈入記憶深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.27,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,勉強靠著你的回憶活下去\N我會更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我自然忘記你的那天\N來臨的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你要原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.19,0:18:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我現在最坦誠的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.14,0:18:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能一直這樣,要忘記他才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她沒有去音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,娘家呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在這個社區裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.05,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這邊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槓龜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是去了三鷹家吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說音無小姐行蹤不明\N是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.00,0:19:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽誰說的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.67,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是問他有沒有看到而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.38,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他一直逼問我,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.95,0:19:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…是真的囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣?為什麼?\N為什麼會發生這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有接到五代的聯絡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.33,0:20:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,五代在搞什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明住在同一個屋簷下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.63,0:20:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況居然沒有察覺\N自己喜歡的女生有異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.81,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是回去一刻館了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打電話問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再去找一遍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好,說不定在哪裡錯過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們往三町目的方向找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了,找到響子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳到底到哪裡去了?\N大家擔心得要命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是去惣一郎的墳前上香…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代怎麼還沒回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他出門的時候\N一副想不開的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.53,0:21:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷,這都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,回來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦,沒有聽到大門打開的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.52,0:21:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事我一定要跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.77,0:21:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的,我雖然明白妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.71,0:21:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.95,0:22:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼\N對了,我們去賞花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上的櫻花很美麗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.82,0:22:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就五代來說\N已經是很棒的表現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,我馬上去準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.37,0:22:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.07,0:22:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天害你擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.87,0:22:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,我真的不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.25,0:22:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得我來這裡,真的是來對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.14,0:23:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好的瘋一瘋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝酒去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.98,0:23:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-站住\N-不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.65,0:23:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女…女高中生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.49,0:23:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,五代說要去女子高中\N當實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.26,0:24:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代被一群可愛的女生迷上\N不知道該如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.26,0:24:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.76,0:24:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「高中女生威力爆發\N對響子發出愛的宣戰佈告」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中女生是很厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.58,0:24:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.08,0:24:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.79,0:24:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.67,0:24:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.24,0:24:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.68,0:24:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.41,0:24:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.25,0:25:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.43,0:25:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.43,0:25:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.61,0:25:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.58,0:25:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy

